title: GET_THRUSTER_SIDE_RCS_THROTTLE
content:
0x1C939E87// GetThrusterSideRcsThrottle
float GET_THRUSTER_SIDE_RCS_THROTTLE(Vehicle jetpack);Parameters:jetpack: The jetpack to check.Returns: Returns a value representing the side RCS (Reaction Control System) throttle of the jetpack. The values range from 0.0 (no throttle) to 1.0 (full throttle).
